Class HDBManager

Object
User
HDBManager
public class HDBManager extends User
Represents a manager in the Build-To-Order system. HDB Managers can create and manage multiple BTO projects, but are only actively assigned to one project at a time. Inherits common user fields from User. Stores a list of all past or created project names.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Javier
